<p>Really glad that you like it! (But yeah I should have done a better job at proofreading :P)</p>
<p>As for mixing up the tenses more and more, yeah, it's a good idea, but it's aslo extremely difficult, and I don't think I can pull that off myself. I think there's a balance between making sense and being disorientating, and what I have now is already a bit confusing for at least part of the readers. I aslo do want to keep at least some order there as I require a repetitive structure for the whole countdown thing. But it is nevertheless a good idea and I think it can be employed in other places :3</p>

